---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Cookie Policy - Woolet"
  description="Cookie Policy for Woolet - Learn how we use cookies and similar technologies."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400">Last updated: February 3, 2026</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              This Cookie Policy explains how Woolet ("we", "our", or "us") uses cookies and similar
              technologies when you visit our website or use our services. It also explains the choices
              you have for managing cookies.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What Are Cookies?</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help
              websites remember your preferences, keep you signed in, and understand how users interact
              with the site.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Cookies We Use</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We use the following types of cookies:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-white">Essential cookies:</strong> Required for core functionality such as authentication, security, and session management.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-white">Preference cookies:</strong> Remember your settings and choices (such as theme preferences).</li>
              <li><strong class="text-white">Analytics cookies:</strong> Help us understand usage patterns and improve performance. These are aggregated and do not directly identify you.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-white">Performance and error monitoring:</strong> Help us diagnose issues and improve reliability.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              We may use third-party services for authentication, analytics, and error monitoring. These
              providers may set their own cookies in accordance with their privacy policies. We do not
              control these cookies directly.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Your Choices</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Disabling some cookies
              may affect the functionality of Woolet.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-2">
              <li>Adjust browser settings to block or delete cookies.</li>
              <li>Use private browsing mode to limit storage of cookies.</li>
              <li>Opt out of analytics cookies where available from the provider.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. We will post the updated policy on
              this page and revise the "Last updated" date above.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-white font-medium">Woolet Support</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Email: privacy@woolet.com</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
